{
  "stem": "19550.5",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 56.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so for instance, they would permit us to take the dead out and bury them in the cemetery, and that enabled us to-- to do certain things by being outside of the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know, like bringing in some food or some medication or-- or through bribery and through chicanery and through whatever we could.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And so there was very little time and opportunity to-- to communication.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Though, in-- in our house, again, it was, you know, a little more so than in the average home as I remember, in that attic, you know, the way we used to [INAUDIBLE] congregate as much as we could.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And, you know, we talked of, obviously, of the immediate problems, and-- and we were in quest of immediate solutions to very real, practical problems, on the one hand.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "On the other hand, obviously we talked about the-- the hopes for an early end to the war before we all [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] die right then and there, so to say.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we talked of resistance, you know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "What could resistance be.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We collected and piled up stones in various areas throughout the ghetto, and then [INAUDIBLE] believe that even when either the opportunity arose or the need arose, we would try to defend ourselves with stones.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] We got ourselves, somehow, the so-called police, and not every-- not even-- really I shouldn't even call it that.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We-- we all-- we all got ourselves a big stick.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "That sort of was our uniform.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And we were hoping that those sticks are going to come in handy.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We-- some of us had a few axes that we were-- that weren't surrendered or weren't discovered.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
